About

Shuhasu Collective

Born from the underground, Shuhasu is a sonic collective exploring the boundaries between electronic music, ritual atmosphere, and psychedelic experience.

We curate immersive events, publish experimental mixes, and cultivate a community of seekers through the transformative power of sound.
